description: Leo Varadkar has apologised for "errors of judgement" over his handling of a confidential document.
title: Leo Varadkar: Irish government wins confidence motion
title_page: Leo Varadkar: Irish government wins confidence motion - BBC News
maintext: He conceded that what he had done was "not best practice" but he had couriered the document to his friend to get wider backing from doctors for the new contract.
